sm.sendNext("Well, my brother Amos is the strongest member of our family. He's so busy training, he's never had time to really find someone special. So, rather than pout about it, he built a special challenge for married couples, in the name of Elias. As you know, Elias sacrificed himself to create a memorial to Cecelia, his true love.  ")
sm.sendSayOkay("The Amorian Challenge is a test of strength for married couples, where they must work together to survive. He can tell you more about it. He's at the far end of Purplewood forest, you can get there by traveling through the Purple Plains.")
